        {
            "title": "大熊貓︱盈盈攜家姐細佬同框見公眾 明早10時派時間票 每組最多50人",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"大熊貓︱盈盈攜家姐細佬同框見公眾 明早10時派時間票 每組最多50人\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/4fdccde8b382fd2cbc5ce51adf54abd1/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250321/_2025032117095133863.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">大熊貓︱盈盈攜家姐細佬同框見公眾 明早10時派時間票 每組最多50人</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>大熊貓龍鳳胎「家姐」、「細佬」明日（22日）起，首度與媽媽「盈盈」在海洋公園「大熊貓之旅」同框亮相，爸爸「樂樂」則繼續獨立與市民見面。展館開放時間將延長至下午4時半，訪客需領取進入展館的「時間票」，按票面列明時間入場。\n\n</p>\n<p>園方明早10點開始在「威威天地」牌坊派「時間票」，由早上10時20分至下午4時20分，每組40至50人一同觀賞，可在棲息地前停留約3分鐘，然後繼續往前方的棲息地探望熊爸「樂樂」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151127/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"經評估後，家姐細佬能與媽媽盈盈在同一空間活動。劉駿軒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/531c34c7ea22dbb84d1a5cd10b22ac3c/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_164554072_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        經評估後，家姐細佬能與媽媽盈盈在同一空間活動。劉駿軒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151126/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"盈盈和家姐細佬明起同框與公眾會面。劉駿軒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cd47c854a9ec8fd91171442772b91314/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_164554072.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        盈盈和家姐細佬明起同框與公眾會面。劉駿軒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151128/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"共享天倫。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6f5a8bf2ba75be633c5c137662928f39/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_164554072_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        共享天倫。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151129/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"盈盈與仔女玩耍。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1cfce13263ac795ab3d07b1ff01de17e/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_164554072_14.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        盈盈與仔女玩耍。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151130/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"親子時間。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/57c9107db705ddcf9648fcc296d9b4d1/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_164554072_15.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        親子時間。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151131/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"家姐細佬在盈盈肚皮翻來覆去。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7dfcb981f2ad10a6d70ab4f06b15e631/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_164554072_16.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        家姐細佬在盈盈肚皮翻來覆去。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151132/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"盈盈「躺平」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2aea5efda1b6cac0ea55affe58923c26/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_164554072_19.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        盈盈「躺平」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151133/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"盈盈與家姐細佬在同一空間活動。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bf29b461be452a08693b302ce76c1951/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_164554072_21.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        盈盈與家姐細佬在同一空間活動。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4151134/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海洋公園寓教於樂部職員盧芷珊(左)、蔡潔茹(右)。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cb4f6e0b8b3a504c1327eb5c5b6c75fc/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250321_164852821.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海洋公園寓教於樂部職員盧芷珊(左)、蔡潔茹(右)。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2><strong>向盈盈學習 提升龍鳳胎體能</strong></h2>\n<p>7個多月大的龍鳳胎上月起公開亮相，但與「盈盈」在同一展館的不同場地。園方日前在社交網站表示，經過護理員的觀察及訓練，牠們仨已經逐漸適應，可以一起在展區活動。海洋公園公司動物及保育部主管祝效忠表示，循序漸進的育幼方式，對於大熊貓寶寶的成長有着舉足輕重的作用。透過逐步引導牠們體驗新事物，讓牠們在豐富多元的環境中向媽媽學習，可提升牠們的體能，並確保牠們身心健康。由媽媽帶領的育幼模式，最能促進大熊貓寶寶健康成長，直至牠們成長至2、3歲，才逐漸離開媽媽獨立生活。\n\n</p>\n<p>另外，剛於1月16日出生的珍稀川金絲猴寶寶是首隻港產雌性川金絲猴、園方稍後將公布牠的名字候選名單，供市民投選。\n\n</p>\n<p>記者：蔡思宇\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
